{"tid":516840,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"[不服來辯]喺ig/fb嗰開post新一年立志嗰堆人正一智障","createTime":"2018-01-01T18:05:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-01T19:14:28.000Z","uid":126603,"like":15,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"53921835a7d16fbe28a370f8d9eb3f8639287a45","tid":516840,"uid":126603,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:05:35.000Z","msg":"一到除夕、元旦成班on9智障喺度發表咩2017年個人回顧、2017感言，又乜閪嘢立志嗰d。<br />\n<br />\n回顧下係好，做下反思，但你唔洗郁d又多謝呢個多謝嗰個，又咩懷念故人。一睇你d文就知你寫文塑造形象多過真係喺度回顧反思。送你呢班人兩隻字：「虛偽」。<br />\n<br />\n最撚on9係嗰班開個post淨係講新一年要有新開始嗰堆人。個post空泛，完全冇內容。根本就喺度跟風，人post你就post。稍為有幾分姿色或者靚仔少少又出呢d post，喺度扮有氣質，有抱負。你真係有料就出返d有內容既post 啦或者做d更有建設性既事啦，唔好為刷like、刷存在感而出post 啦。<br />\n<br />\n你老味唔係新一年你就唔會有新既開始？<br />\n<br />\n你真係想有新開始就唔該你埋頭苦幹去做好d嘢佢啦柒頭。"},{"pid":"19f9e04dc7c0fb54264c8ab43359b772c58908fb","tid":516840,"uid":135390,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"樓主冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a27aa4708ccd4a6ca934ea84e7f3b701413d948","tid":516840,"uid":129039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:15:09.000Z","msg":"agger"},{"pid":"169035a978fb64de9adcafc54776e76d3bfc86e5","tid":516840,"uid":126603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"19f9e04dc7c0fb54264c8ab43359b772c58908fb","tid":516840,"uid":135390,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:11:13.000Z","msg":"樓主冇朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:19:11.000Z","msg":"屌嗰班出廢post既on9又關有冇朋友事？你邊隻字見到我講緊朋友？<br />\n咩邏輯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？<br />\n<br />\n你fb/ig入面係咪個個都係你朋友<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ？"},{"pid":"958baed79717e0b47a81d561b1b2655d957a17e5","tid":516840,"uid":14625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T18:20:42.000Z","msg":"私人地方post野都要俾人屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.